                    <span>I recently finished school and was in the process of opening an agency of my own, with only my wife for a part-time evening co-worker. This book helped me side step many costly mistakes that any beginner could easily make. The detail this book provided, exploring every aspect of the advertising process, is worth its weight in gold. Excellent job.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">It's decent, but the radio part is limited</div>
